data.description: Paradise is here! This turnkey 4.8 acre ranch is like living in a dream everyday! Make this life your new reality. Enjoy very minimal power bills and generous credits with a solar system with no lease and a 40K value paid off by the seller at closing. Live practically off the grid with a private water well with no water bills. House is very well maintained. Property has numerous beautiful trees and custom made bird enclosures and a farm to table garden where you can enjoy fresh grown food and even grow food for animals like ducks and chickens which are also living on the property and negotiable with the sale. You got your own private Frisbee golf course. Panoramic views of the desert and mountains surround you. Very motivated sellers. Make an appt today to come see this hidden gem and make this relaxing life yours! Did I mention the property is fully fenced and gated for your privacy and quiet enjoyment! Upgraded windows keep the home cozy warm in the winter and energy efficient!
